data.title: MB 101813 Opt
data.meta_description:
Mb 101813 Opt - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. The document discusses several topics:
1. Mayors in Bohol appealed for immediate food, water, medicine and fuel assistance after their towns were devastated by a 7.2 magnitude earthquake. They fear a possible food and water crisis as rescue efforts have yet to fully reach some localities. 
2. The Supreme Court will consolidate all investigations into the "Ma'am Arlene" influence peddling case to avoid confusion from multiple parallel probes. 
3. The Bulacan governor warned of a potential disaster if the Angat Dam, which sits above an active fault line, were to collapse in a major earthquake.
